{"tid":969722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未補價居屋 VS 私樓","createTime":"2019-01-05T09:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:13:00.000Z","uid":82466,"like":8,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4905298cc295b0ac0e31eb061834fc1e0456c76d","tid":969722,"uid":82466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"正評:<br />\n(綠表)交還公屋，換二手600萬未補價居屋(3房6XX呎實用) 同屋企人住<br />\n首期5% $300,000 印花稅$180,000  25年月供大約$25XXX(自己供一半)<br />\n加埋攞$480,000出黎，未計裝修<br />\n**優點 換大左 又可以裝修靚D 痴住屋企住<br />\n缺點 冇撚左間2000蚊公屋<br />\n<br />\n負評:<br />\n私樓，420萬，30年樓市中心(2房300呎實用)自己住<br />\n首期大約15%約$600,000 印花稅$110,000萬 30年月供大約$14XXX(自己供)<br />\n加埋攞$710,000出黎，未計裝修<br />\n**優點 自己住又得 收租又得 彈性D<br />\n缺點 一開頭攞多左錢出黎 又唔可以痴住屋企住"},{"pid":"0cfe21fb6db15b825b0b5bd585026acc9071180a","tid":969722,"uid":82466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"長得濟 冇人睇"},{"pid":"28b91c46aa1b2d6b33005cb3c74034743dfe2356","tid":969722,"uid":43530,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"買私樓放租等人幫你供再痴屋企住公屋"},{"pid":"b26b6e003e14f89ecaedf40ae9e11c7c01b34d2a","tid":969722,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"繼續住公屋儲錢<br />\n等樓市爆再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f23459e8d522425d6a7beef8a882bfa3b1becb2","tid":969722,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"住公屋等樓價爆就得"},{"pid":"12b6e8de2f9f5dbc6e5e4c990a9212a81b4fa497","tid":969722,"uid":38301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"到底你想痴屋企定唔痴屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔急住，我會揀買私樓出租<br />\n幾年後結婚先收番嚟住"},{"pid":"316b940211b8717fb4f289f8efacd102b3df5dde","tid":969722,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28b91c46aa1b2d6b33005cb3c74034743dfe2356","tid":969722,"uid":43